Package: git-subrepo
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, git (>= 2.8), bash (>= 4)
Description: GIT Submodule alternative
 This is a GIT Submodule alternative written by Ingy döt Net.
 .
 This git command "clones" an external git repo into a subdirectory
 of your repo. Later on, upstream changes can be pulled in, and local
 changes can be pushed back. Simple.
 .
 WWW: https://github.com/ingydotnet/git-subrepo
